reviewText:
Fantastic picture and sound quality for a VHS tape! Only 4 tracks, but they are all excellent!
Don't hesitate!

Just got my tape and ran to my closet to get my old vcr out of there since they don't make this on dvd, just to find Martha Davis and her group couldn't do a better performance, these videos really took me back to my college years and the MTV days, there's only a few copies left, if you can buy it, i strongly recommend it.
